# Moonraker Host Admin Service — env
# Copy to /opt/moonraker-admin/.env, fill, chmod 600, chown mradmin:mradmin.
#
# This AGENT_API_KEY is the ADMIN token, distinct from the agent container's
# AGENT_API_KEY. Generate with: openssl rand -hex 32.
# Do NOT put this value in Vercel — only the user + durable password manager
# should know it.
AGENT_API_KEY=
